data.description: SOLAR PANEL HOME! Welcome to the Ultimate Gamers' Haven in the heart of Wesley Chapel, FL! Step into a world where excitement meets innovation in this stunning 4-bedroom home with a den, 2.5 bathrooms, occupying a prime corner lot. With a generous 2,861 sqft of living space, this home is more than just a living space – it's a masterpiece of comfort, entertainment, and cutting-edge design. Be prepared to be enchanted by the artistic charm that surrounds you, "Let's A Go!". Greeted by a custom painted mural in the loft, created by a professional artist, this home is a true testament to creativity and imagination. The vibrant colors and intricate details transport you to a realm of unlimited possibilities, making every moment spent here a truly unique experience. For gaming enthusiasts, this residence has been thoughtfully designed to fulfill your every desire. Imagine hosting epic gaming sessions in the spacious living area, where the open layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining space, and kitchen. The kitchen boasts top-of-the-line appliances, including a smart kitchen faucet and oven, ample counter space, and sleek modern finishes – perfect for whipping up energizing snacks during intense gaming marathons or hosting gourmet feasts for friends and family. That's how you Princess! The smart features extend to the living space with 5.1 surround pre-wiring and smart light switches, bulbs, and fans, allowing you to create the perfect ambiance for your gaming adventures. Retreat to the sanctuary of your choice from the 4 bedrooms and a den, each designed for comfort and relaxation. The master suite is DOWNSTAIRS and offers a tranquil escape, with an ensuite bathroom that features a luxurious soaking tub and a rejuvenating shower. The marble design tile in the office and master bedroom exudes elegance and style. Venture outdoors to the expansive corner lot, complete with a backyard fence for privacy and security. The smart sprinkler system keeps your lawn vibrant and lush, while the additional in-home security cameras (2 downstairs, 1 upstairs, 1 on the back porch) provide peace of mind. The garage is equipped with racks for efficient storage and an epoxy floor for a polished look. The smart garage door adds convenience to your lifestyle. And that's not all – this home comes with a full solar system and a soft water system, showcasing its commitment to sustainability and wellbeing. Located in the sought-after Epperson Ranch Crystal Lagoon community, you'll enjoy an array of amenities including the dazzling Crystal Lagoon, perfect for swimming and leisure activities. Conveniently near top-rated schools. Epperson North HOA fee: $225/quarter (includes Ultra-Fi: 400+mbps), Crystal Lagoon Membership Fee: $130/quarter. Nearby Elementary Schools: Innovation Preparatory Academy, Watergrass Elementary School. Nearest high schools: Kirkland Academy of Innovation HS, Wesley Chapel HS. Epperson North Lagoon Community offers unique amenities, including Crystal Lagoon access, Elam Park, King Lake dock, and more. Close to KRATE, Tampa, airport, Orlando. Your next level of living awaits! This home is more than just a dwelling – it's a canvas for your dreams, an arena for your gaming conquests, and a testament to the extraordinary. Don't miss out on the chance to own this remarkable slice of paradise. Contact us today for an exclusive tour and experience the magic firsthand. Your next level of living awaits! Mamma Mia!
